<h1>You’re invited to <%= @invitation.organization.name %></h1>

<p><%= @invitation.invited_by.name %> invited you to join <%= @invitation.organization.name %> as <%= @invitation.role.humanize.downcase %>.</p>

<p>Accept the invitation to join the organization workspace and take your place on the semester roster.</p>

<p><%= link_to "Accept invitation", @acceptance_url %></p>

<p>This invitation expires on <%= @invitation.expires_at.to_date.to_fs(:long) %>.</p>
